name: Team Weekly
description:
A place for your team to gather to share cheesy quotes, announcements, work, and inspiration. Topped off with a team question game.


Instructions:


  1. Add a new row each week.
  2. Remove photos of Leonardo DiCaprio (optional)
  3. Add announcements
  4. Invite others to share WIP or final projects
  5. Check out inspiration
  6. Play the question game


Created by the Product Studio team at VICE.
